            "text": "<p>A FARM-TO-FLASK INITIATIVE<br/><br/>Okanagan Spirits Craft Distillery celebrates their local partners who truly champion the craft local renaissance in authentic spirits production. These hospitality sector leaders support local and highlight true Craft BC Spirits in their cocktail programs to enhance the local BC experience for their patrons. We work with great partners across the Okanagan and BC to ensure the Craft BC movement keeps growing.<br/><br/>We hope that you choose to support these amazing local businesses as they have joined the Farm-to-Flask movement and supported us.<br/></p>",
